{"uuid": "43fed708-70d0-4152-8cd1-3f29ded91d5a", "id": 56070, "date": "2025-03-01T04:00:14", "date_gmt": "2025-03-01T12:00:14", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=56070"}, "modified": "2025-02-24T15:50:40", "modified_gmt": "2025-02-24T23:50:40", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-march-1-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/03/01/kingdom-of-days-march-1-2/", "title": {"rendered": "Kingdom of Days: March 1"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><em><strong>New for 2025:\u00a0</strong>No updates</em></p>\n<p>Note: This is a strange date in history: Bruce rarely cancels shows, but on this date he cancelled shows three years running!</p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>A scheduled date in San Jose opening for Paul Butterfield is cancelled due to low ticket sales.</p>\n<p><strong>1974:</strong> Bruce cancels a show at the New Jersey State Theater due to illness. Who knew Bruce graduated from Rutgers? (The journalist below sure doesn&#8217;t.) Disappointed Springsteen fans ask for their money back; the theater obliges and throws in a bonus.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"16396\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-03-01/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1974-03-01.jpg?fit=567%2C400&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"567,400\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1582570017&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-03-01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1974-03-01.jpg?fit=300%2C212&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1974-03-01.jpg?fit=567%2C400&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-16396 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1974-03-01-300x212.jpg?resize=758%2C536\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1974-03-01.jpg?resize=300%2C212&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1974-03-01.jpg?w=567&amp;ssl=1 567w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"49003\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/the_central_new_jersey_home_news_sat__mar_2__1974_/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?fit=2134%2C1266&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2134,1266\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?fit=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?fit=758%2C449&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-49003\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?resize=758%2C450&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?w=2134&amp;ssl=1 2134w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?resize=1024%2C607&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?resize=768%2C456&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?resize=1536%2C911&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The_Central_New_Jersey_Home_News_Sat__Mar_2__1974_.jpg?resize=2048%2C1215&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"25388\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-03-01a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1974-03-01a.jpg?fit=546%2C1835&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"546,1835\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-03-01a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1974-03-01a.jpg?fit=89%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1974-03-01a.jpg?fit=305%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-25388\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1974-03-01a.jpg?resize=758%2C2555&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"2555\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:</strong> Yet another cancellation, this one in Syracuse, due to a conflict with mixing sessions for <em>Born to Run</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>1980:</strong> Bruce sits in with the David Johansen Group at The Fast Lane in Asbury Park, joining the band for &#8220;Personality Crisis&#8221; and &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/11/29/cover-me-lucille/\">Lucille</a>.&#8221;</p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>Friday Night Videos airs Part 2 of its &#8220;Private Reel&#8221; profile of Bruce.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"80s TV | Friday Night Videos | Bruce Springsteen interview | 1985\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JM4oYHfP5nc?start=1&#038;feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1990:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and Bob Dylan make a guest appearance with Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers at the Forum in Inglewood, California.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Tom Petty with Bruce Springsteen - &quot;Travelin\u00b4 band/ I\u00b4m crying&quot;\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LG2mygv6WPs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"25390\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1990-03-01-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1990-03-01.jpg?fit=312%2C934&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"312,934\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1582570800&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1990-03-01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1990-03-01.jpg?fit=100%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1990-03-01.jpg?fit=312%2C934&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-25390\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1990-03-01.jpg?resize=438%2C1314&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"438\" height=\"1314\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1994:\u00a0</strong>At the Grammy Awards, Bruce appears with B.B. King, Bonnie Raitt, Steve Winwood and others during a medley tribute to Curtis Mayfield. Watch their performance below.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Curtis Mayfield All-Star Jam\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AjM2KHrNUxk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><strong>1995:</strong> Bruce performs &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2021/06/30/roll-of-the-dice-streets-of-philadelphia/\">Streets of Philadelphia</a>&#8221; and wins Grammys for Best Rock Song, Best Male Rock Vocal Performance, Song of the Year, and Best Song Written Specifically for a Motion Picture or for Television. The only nomination for which he doesn&#8217;t take home the award is for Record of the Year. Check out the footage of the awards, post-ceremony interviews and more below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-HclHJdZx-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/HclHJdZx?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen wins awards for &quot;Streets of Philadelphia&quot;\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5_cloJH4slM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Bruce Springsteen &quot;Streets of Philadelphia&quot; Grammy Interview\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/W5OExj0BakE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div id=\"v-KNpyCgB4-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/KNpyCgB4?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"1995:  BRUCE SPRINGSTEEN &amp; wife PATTI leave Grammy party\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/g8k45X2-0Wg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"25392\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1995-03-01/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?fit=2585%2C1196&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2585,1196\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1995-03-01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?fit=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?fit=758%2C351&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-25392\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?resize=758%2C351&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"351\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?resize=300%2C139&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?resize=1024%2C474&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?resize=768%2C355&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?resize=1536%2C711&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?resize=2048%2C948&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/1995-03-01.png?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1996:\u00a0</strong>If press reports are accurate, Bruce gets a workout in at Marco&#8217;s Gym in Edinburgh during an off-day on his solo acoustic tour. The timing is odd, however, since he played in Birmingham last night and will perform in Newcastle tomorrow. His Edinburgh show isn&#8217;t for another two days. Perhaps he&#8217;s making Edinburgh his base of operations for this leg of the tour.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"48973\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/daily_record_sat__mar_2__1996_/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?fit=2560%2C1660&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2560,1660\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?fit=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C492&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-48973\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C492&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"492\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?resize=300%2C194&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C664&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C498&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C996&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1328&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Daily_Record_Sat__Mar_2__1996_-scaled.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2003:\u00a0</strong>Bruce sets a Ticketmaster record, becoming the first artist to sell tickets for seven stadium shows in a single day. Before the day is out, Bruce will sell more than 300,000 tickets to his summer residency at Giants Stadium.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"16399\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2003-03-01/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2003-03-01.jpg?fit=691%2C604&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"691,604\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1582571203&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2003-03-01\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2003-03-01.jpg?fit=300%2C262&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2003-03-01.jpg?fit=691%2C604&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-16399 aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2003-03-01-300x262.jpg?resize=758%2C662\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"662\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2003-03-01.jpg?resize=300%2C262&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2003-03-01.jpg?resize=660%2C577&amp;ssl=1 660w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2003-03-01.jpg?w=691&amp;ssl=1 691w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2014:</strong> Bruce plays the first of two shows in Auckland, New Zealand. He opens with an acoustic cover of Lorde&#8217;s &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/04/25/cover-me-royals/\">Royals</a>,&#8221; tour debuts &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2022/06/23/roll-of-the-dice-loose-end/\">Loose Ends</a>,&#8221; and plays the full\u00a0<em>Born in the U.S.A. </em>album.\u00a0 This show has an opening act: Jimmy Barnes, who recorded Steve Van Zandt&#8217;s &#8220;Ride the Night Away&#8221; on his 1985 album,\u00a0<em>For the Working Class Man</em>. Steve makes a guest appearance during Jimmy&#8217;s set to join him for that song.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Ride The Night Away - Jimmy Barnes and Little Steven - Mt Smart Stadium, Auckland 1-3-2014\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/n7PagtsHHbs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div id=\"v-eYWAhM3R-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/eYWAhM3R?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Royals (Live at Mount Smart Stadium, Auckland, NZ - 03/01/14 - Official Audio)\" width=\"758\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OBIAKHw5y4Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-v